high_descs: walk to face counter to left of sink
wash spatula in left hand sink, pick up spatula from sink
anns.task_desc: put washed spatula on kitchen table

high_descs: Walk forwards and to your right until you reach the sink on your right.
Pick up the spatula that is next to the toaster.
Walk to your right and closer to the sink.
Place the spatula into the sink, fill the sink with water, and then drain the sink.
Pick up the spatula again and take a right, and then right again to the white table.
Place the spatula down next to the spoon on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Wash off the spatula so you can place it on the white table.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the sink, turn right to face the toaster on the counter, left of the sink.
Pick up the spatula on the counter.
Bring the spatula to the left sink.
Wash the spatula in the left sink with water.
Bring the cleaned spatula to the table behind you with the coffee machine on it.
Put the cleaned spatula on the table, in front of the soap.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spatula on the table.
